8. Es el mismo valor la variable sum en estos loops:

jshell> for (int i = 0; i < 10; ++i){sum += i;}

jshell> sum
sum ==> 45

jshell> i
i ==> 0

jshell> for (int i = 0; i < 10; ++i){sum += i;}

jshell> sum
sum ==> 90

jshell> i
i ==> 0

jshell> for (int i = 0; i < 10; ++i){sum += i;}

jshell> sum
sum ==> 135

jshell> i
i ==> 0

jshell> sum = 0
sum ==> 0

jshell> for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++){sum += i;}

jshell> sum
sum ==> 45

jshell> i
i ==> 0

jshell> for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++){sum += i;}

jshell> sum
sum ==> 90

jshell> i
i ==> 0

jshell> for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++){sum += i;}

jshell> sum
sum ==> 135

jshell> i
i ==> 0